# API Behavior Doc – Definition of Done (Admin)

Sau khi implement xong một feature trong `admin-service`, **bắt buộc** tạo file API behavior doc tại:

```
docs/api_fe_behavior/admin_api_fe_behavior/<FeatureName>-api-and-behavior.md
```

Ví dụ:

- `AuthorizeAdminApi-api-and-behavior.md`
- `SuspendUser-api-and-behavior.md`
- `RemoveProduct-api-and-behavior.md`
- `PublishAdminEvents-api-and-behavior.md`

**Lưu ý:** Feature chỉ delegate Auth (vd. `FR_AdminLogin`) vẫn nên có doc mô tả contract Auth + cách Admin FE dùng JWT — không bỏ qua vì Admin Service không có endpoint.

## Nội dung bắt buộc

```markdown
# <Feature Name> – API & Behavior

## 1. Business Goal
## 2. API Contract
- Method, URL: /admin/api/v1/... (hoặc Auth URL nếu delegate)
- Auth: Bearer JWT (required/optional)
- Required permission (nếu có)
- Params / body

## 3. Response – Success
## 4. Response – Error
| HTTP | code string | Mô tả |
| 401  | ADMIN-401 | ... |
| 403  | ADMIN-403 | ... |

## 5. Business Rules
- admin_id từ JWT
- reason bắt buộc (nếu destructive)
- audit / moderation logs
- outbox event (nếu có)

## 6. Edge Cases
## 7. Data Dependencies
- PostgreSQL table(s) trong admin_db
- Owner service / event (Auth, Commerce, Social)

## 8. FE Integration Notes
- Admin portal gọi Auth vs Admin
- Permission/role hiển thị trên UI
```

Tham chiếu format mẫu: `docs/api_fe_behavior/commerce_api_fe_behavior/RemoveProductByAdmin-api-and-behavior.md`.

## Definition of Done

- [ ] Code đúng architecture (delivery → application → domain → infrastructure)
- [ ] API envelope chuẩn (`docs/engineering_rules/api-standard.md`)
- [ ] Error code `ADMIN-*`
- [ ] `FR_AuthorizeAdminApi`: unauthorized không chạy mutation
- [ ] Audit/enforcement/moderation logs + outbox theo FR
- [ ] Unit test business logic chính (authorization, validation)
- [ ] Integration test cho API/DB khi cần
- [ ] File `docs/api_fe_behavior/admin_api_fe_behavior/<Feature>-api-and-behavior.md` đầy đủ
- [ ] Không business logic trong Controller/DTO
- [ ] Không log token/password/secret trong payload audit
